## Production Issues Encountered Today

| Issue | Impact | Resolution |
|---|---|---|
| `ERROR 42883: operator does not exist: uuid = text` while running 034 migration | `order_shipments` migration failed | Updated RLS comparisons to explicit safe casts and made policy creation rerun-safe |
| `PGRST200` relationship missing between `orders` and `order_shipments` | Buyer Orders screen failed to load, order list/details inaccessible | Added hotfix migration 035 to restore FK and adjusted app query path with fallback |
| `ERROR 0A000: cannot alter type of a column used in a policy definition` during 035 run | Blocked `order_id` type conversion from text to uuid | Updated 035 to drop dependent policies before type change and recreate them after migration |

